hadiths[24]{hadithnumber,text}:
2695,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (tarkey mein) na koi Dinar chhoda na dirham, na koi bakri na oont aur na aap ney kisi chiz key barey mein wasiyat ki."
2696,"Hazrat Talha bin Musrif (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi chiz key barey mein wasiyat farmaai thi? unhoney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ko wasiyat ka hukm kaisey diya? unhoney farmaya : aap ney Allah ki kitab (par amal kerney) ki wasiyat ki thi. Hazrat Huzail bin Shurehbil (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : kya Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key wasi ko (jo Hazrat Ali ko qarar diya jata hai) nazar andaz kar key Ameer bin saktey they? Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) to ye chahtey they ke unhen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi key haq mein wasiyat mil jati, chahey wo un ki naak mein nakel dal leta."
2697,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt aaya aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka saans atak raha tha, us waqt aap ney sab sey ziyada ye wasiyat ki : namaz aur tumharey mamlook (ghulaam)."
2698,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aakhiri kalam ye tha : namaz aur tumharey mamlook (ghulaam)."
2699,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ka ye haq nahin ke agar uskey paas koi aisi chiz mojud ho jis key barey mein wo wasiyat karna chahta ho to wo do raaten bhi is haal mein guzaarey ke uski wasiyat uskey barey mein likhi hui uskey paas mojud na ho."
2700,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mehroom wo hai jo apni wasiyat karney sey mehroom raha."
2701,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs wasiyat kar key faut huwa, wo sidhi raah par aur sunnat tareeqey par (amal karta huwa) faut huwa. wo taqwe aur shahadat ki maut mara. aur us haal mein mara ke uski bakhshish ho chuki thi."
2702,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis musalman key paas koi qabile wasiyat chiz ho, usey ye haq nahin ke do raaten bhi us haal mein guzaarey ke uski wasiyat uskey paas likhi hui mojud na ho."
2703,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney waris ko tarka deney sey bhageyga (aisi wasiyat kerega jis sey jayez waris ko hissey na miley ya uskey asal hissey sey kam miley) to Allah Taala qiyamat key din usey uski jannat ki meeras sey mehroom farma dega."
2704,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi sattar saal tak nek logon waley kaam karta rehta hai, phir jab (martey waqt) wasiyat karta hai to wasiyat mein na insafi karta hai, is tarah uska anjam burey kaam par hota hai, chunanche wo jahannam mein chala jata hai. aur eik aadmi sattar saal tak burey logon waley kaam karta rehta hai, phir (martey waqt) wasiyat mein insaf sey kaam leta hai to is tarah uska anjam nek kaam par hota hai, chunanche wo jannat mein chala jata hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : agar chaho to ye aayat padh lo : ( تِلْكَ حُدُوْدُ اللّٰهِ padhi. وَمَنْ يُّطِعِ اللّٰهَ وَرَسُوْلَه يُدْخِلْهُ جَنّٰتٍ تَجْرِيْ مِنْ تَحْتِھَا الْاَنْھٰرُ خٰلِدِيْنَ فِيْھَا padhi. وَ ذٰلِكَ الْفَوْزُ الْعَظِيْمُ وَ مَنْ يَّعْصِ اللّٰهَ وَ رَسُوْلَه وَ يَتَعَدَّ حُدُوْدَه يُدْخِلْهُ نَارًا خَالِدًا فِيْھَا padhi. وَلَه عَذَابٌ مُّهِيْنٌ ) ye haden Allah ki (muqarrar ki hui) hain aur jo Allah Taala ki aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki farma bradri kerey. usey Allah Taala jannaton mein ley jaeyga jinkey nichey nehren beh rahi hain, jin mein wo hamesha rahengey, aur ye bahut badi kamiyabi hai. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala ki aur uskey Rasool ki na farmani karey aur uski (muqarrara) hadon sey aagey nikley, usey wo jahannam mein dal dega jis mein wo hamesha rahega. aur uskey liye ruswa kun azab hai."
2705,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid (Hazrat Qurra bin Ayas bin Hilal Muzni (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski wafat ka waqt aaya to usney wasiyat ki aur uski wasiyat Allah ki kitab key mutabiq thi, uska ye amal uski zindagi mein tarak shuda zakat ka kaffara bin jaeyga."
2706,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz ki : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey bataaiye ke merey husne-suluk ka mustahiq kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan ! qism hai terey baap ( key rab) ki ! tujhey zarur bataunga . teri maa (terey husne-suluk ki sab sey ziyada mustahiq hai.) usney kaha : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : phir teri maa. usney kaha : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : phir teri maa. usney kaha : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : tera baap. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! mujhey merey maal key barey mein bataaiye ke main is mein sey kis tarah sadqa karun? aap ney farmaya : haan! qism hai Allah ki! tujhey zarur bataunga. (wo is tarah hai ke) to us waqt sadqa karey jab to tandurust ho aur maal sey mohabbat rakhta ho, tujhey zinda rehney ki ummid ho aur faqr ka andesha ho. (ye sadqa ka sahih waqt hai) aur muakhkhar na karna yahan tak key jab teri jaan yahan (halaq tak) pahunch jaey, phir to kahey : mera maal falan ko dey dena, mera maal falan ko bhi dey dena. wo to unhi ka ho chuka, agar-che tujhey ye (haqeeqat) nagawar mehsus ho."
2707,"Hazrat Busr bin Jahash qarshii (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni hatheli par luaab Mubarak dala , phir apni sabab ungli (uski taraf isharay key tor par) rakhi aur farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : Adam key betey ! to mujhey kaisey aajiz kar sakta hai, halanke mainey tujhey us jaisi chiz sey paida farmaya, phir jab teri jaan yahan pahunch jati hai, ye kehtey huye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney halaq ki taraf ishara farmaya, tab to kehta hai : main sadqa karta hun . ab sadqey ka waqt kahan hai?"
2708,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kya, unhoney farmaya : Fateh Makka key saal main bimar ho gaya yahan tak key maut key kinarey pahunch gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat key liye tashrif laye . mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mera maal bahut ziyada hai aur meri waris meri sirf eik beti hai to kya main apna do tihai maal sadqa kar dun? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin . mainey kaha : aadha ? farmaya : nahin, mainey kaha : tihai ? farmaya : tihai ( jayez hai) aur tihai bhi ziyada hai. tera apney warison ko khushhal chhodna unhen muflis chhod janey sey behtar hai ke wo logon key aagey haath phelatey pherein ."
2709,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney tum par ye sadqa kya hai ke wafat key waqt tumhen tihai maal (mein wasiyat ka haq) dey diya hai taake tumharey nek aamal mein izafa ho jaey ."
2710,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( Allah Taala farmata hai :) aey Adam key betey! do cheezen (mainey tujhey di hain), un mein sey eik bhi terey haath mein nahin thi. mainey terey maal mein us waqt tera hissa muqarrar kar diya jab main teri saans band karta hun. (ye isliye) taake tujhey pak saaf kar dun aur (doosri chiz) teri zindagi key khatam ho janey key baad merey bandon ka tujh par namaz janaza ada karna."
2711,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey ye baat pasand hai ke log teesrey hissey ko kam kar key chauthey hissey ki wasiyat kya karen kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teesra hissa eik badi miqdaar hai. ya farmaya : teesra hissa ziyada hai."
2712,"Hazrat Amr bin kharija (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney logon sey khitab farmaya jabke aap apni sawari (oontni) par sawar they. aur aap ki sawari khub jugaali kar rahi thi. aur uska luaab merey kandhon key darmiyan (pusht par) gir raha tha. (us moqey par) aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney har waris ko tarkey ka hissa taqseem kar key dey diya hai, lihaza waris key liye wasiyat jayez nahin. bacha bistar waley ka hai aur badkaar key liye pathar hain. jo shakhs apney baap key siwa kisi aur ka beta honey ka dawa karey ya apney azad karney walon key siwa kisi aur ki taraf azadi ki nisbat karey to is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki lanat hai. uska na farz qubul hoga aur na nafl. ya farmaya : na nafl qubul hoga na farz."
2713,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Sudey bin Ajlan) Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney khutba Mubarak mein ye farmatey suna : Allah Taala ney har haq waley ko uska haq dey diya hai, lihaza waris key liye koi wasiyat nahin."
2714,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni key (munh key) nichey khada tha jabkey mujh par uska luaab gir raha tha. (us waqt) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna : Allah Taala ney har haq waley ko uska haq dey diya hai, lihaza waris key liye koi wasiyat nahin ."
2715,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wasiyat puri karney sey pehley qarz ada karney ka hukm diya aur tum ye aayat padhtey ho : ( مِنْ بَعْدِ وَصِيَّةٍ يُّوْصِيْ بِھَآ اَوْ دَيْنٍ ) , us wasiyat key baad jo wo wasiyat karey ya qarz key baad .) Nisa, 4:11 (aur sagey bhai , eik maa key betey waris hongey , soteley bhai nahin ."
2716,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya : mera walid faut ho gaya hai aur usney maal chhoda hai lekin wasiyat nahin ki. agar main uski taraf sey sadqa karun to kya uskey gunah maaf ho jaeyngey ? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan ."
2717,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : meri walida achcha faut ho gaee hain aur unhoney wasiyat nahin ki. aur mera khayal hai ke agar unhen baatcheet karney ka moqey milta to sadqa kartin. agar main unki taraf sey sadqa karun to kya unhen sawab milega, aur kya mujhey bhi sawab milega? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan."
2718,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : merey paas kuch nahin (guzaara nahin hota) na merey paas koi maal hai, albatta eik yatim meri kafalat mein hai, uska maal hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney yatim key maal mein sey kha liya kar lekin fuzul kharchi na karna, aur (uskey maal sey) maal na kamana. aur ghaaliban ye bhi farmaya : uskey maal key zariey sey apna maal na bachaana."
